events.name: 第一部ラスト　侵入

parameters: \n<Thief>Huh? Maybe it's some animal's cry or something?

\n<Thief>No, it's more like a distant rumbling... What
the!?

Ugh... even through the barrier, that was a
tremendous shock. Thank goodness for the
cushioning.\n<Serena>
\n<Thief>You there! Who the hell are you!?
\n<Serena>I have no name to give to the likes of you!

...Phew. That was quite a rough method, even for
me, but it seems I've managed to infiltrate
successfully.\n<Serena>

However, this will cause a commotion soon. I must
find Lady Erika without delay.\n<Serena>

The floors and walls are quite damaged... It's
said to be the remains of an old fort...\n<Serena>

Hmm... This staircase won't do, I can hear
people's voices. Is there somewhere I can descend
without being noticed?\n<Serena>
